title: Pampers | Mother's Day #ThanksBaby
description:
When a baby is born, a mom is born. And from that moment, she is never the same. Happy Mother's Day from Pampers. 

This Pampers video is a Mother's Day tribute to mother and baby. #ThanksBaby for making us moms.

transcripts:
Dear Henry,

From the first moment I saw you, I knew I would never be the same. When you were born, I was born. Because you made me a mom and as you grew, I also grew. To be as good as possible. For you forever.

Love,

Mom
